:

1. *Brinem* se da će uspeti da ostvari svoj cilj. (I worry that they will succeed in achieving their goal.)
2. Njegova ljubav je tako *brinula* o njoj. (His love was so caring for her.)
3. Ona je uvek bila tu da *brine* o njoj. (She was always there to take care of her.)
4. Oni su *brinuli* o svojoj deci. (They were looking after their children.)
5. *Brinem* se da će sve biti u redu. (I'm worried that everything will be okay.)